# Aws Lambda + S3 + Bedrock

![Alt text](data:image/png;base64,)

Components usage:
* Amazon Api Gateway to call the lambda function from Postman
* Lambda, receive the prompt, call the model in bedrock
* S3, to save the generated text
* Cloud Watcher to see the logs

Use case - flow:
* Prompt - ask to generate a blog post
* Using Postman we call the Api Gateway
* The gateway api trigger the lambda
* The lambda get the prompt, call the bedrock asking for the prompt
* The lambda get the respose of bedrock save it to s3
* The lambda returns the response of bedrock to the user
